name: Flower of Life Laser Engraved Selenite Plates
description:
The Flower of Life is laser engraved onto these polished selenite plates, available in hexagon or round. Selenite plates are great for charging your crystals and resetting their energies.


Do not submerge in water, as selenite could disintegrate. Wipe clean with a damp cloth.


Diameter 6" x .75-1" thick


Made in Morocco
